## 8. Water-Energy Nexus — Desalination

```elixir
# RO desalination plant
ro = EnergyX.WaterEnergy.Desalination.ro_energy(%{
  feed_pressure_bar: 65.0, recovery: 0.45,
  eta_pump: 0.85, erd_efficiency: 0.96, source: :seawater})

lcow = EnergyX.WaterEnergy.Desalination.lcow(%{
  capacity_m3_d: 50_000.0, capex_usd_m3_per_day: 1400.0,
  sec_kwh_m3: ro.sec_with_erd_kwh_m3, elec_price: 0.08,
  hours_d: 20.0, discount_rate: 0.06, lifetime_yr: 25})

IO.puts("""
SWRO Desalination Plant — 50,000 m³/day:
  SEC (no ERD):    #{ro.sec_without_erd_kwh_m3} kWh/m³
  SEC (with ERD):  #{ro.sec_with_erd_kwh_m3} kWh/m³ (#{ro.erd_saving_pct}% saving)
  Benchmark:       #{ro.benchmark.typical} kWh/m³ (typical)

  LCOW = USD #{lcow.lcow_usd_m3}/m³
  CAPEX total:     USD #{trunc(lcow.capex_total_usd / 1_000_000)} M
""")
```

