## 9. Transportation — EV vs ICE Full Comparison

```elixir
tco = EnergyX.Transportation.ElectricVehicle.tco_comparison(%{
  ev_price: 35_000, ice_price: 25_000,
  ev_kwh_100km: 17.0, ice_l_100km: 7.5,
  elec_price: 0.14, fuel_price: 1.65,
  km_yr: 15_000,
  ev_maintenance_yr: 350, ice_maintenance_yr: 900,
  years: 5})

IO.puts("""
EV vs ICE Vehicle — 5-Year TCO (15,000 km/yr):
  EV 5-yr TCO:    USD #{tco.ev_5yr_tco_usd}
  ICE 5-yr TCO:   USD #{tco.ice_5yr_tco_usd}
  EV saves:       USD #{tco.ev_saves_usd}
  Breakeven:      Year #{tco.breakeven_years}
  Annual fuel saving: USD #{tco.annual_fuel_saving}/yr
""")

# Road load breakdown
load = EnergyX.Transportation.ElectricVehicle.road_load_power(%{
  mass_kg: 1800.0, speed_km_h: 120.0, cd: 0.27,
  a_frontal_m2: 2.4, crr: 0.012, grade_pct: 0.0})

IO.puts("""
EV Road Load at 120 km/h (1800 kg, Cd=0.27):
  Aero drag:       #{load.aero_power_kw} kW  (#{Float.round(load.aero_power_kw / load.total_power_kw * 100, 0) |> trunc()}%)
  Rolling resist:  #{load.rolling_power_kw} kW
  Total:           #{load.total_power_kw} kW
  Consumption:     #{load.consumption_kwh_100km} kWh/100km
""")
```

