## 10. Unit Conversions & Constants Reference

```elixir
IO.puts("Physical Constants (EnergyX.Constants):")
IO.puts("  Stefan-Boltzmann σ: #{EnergyX.Constants.stefan_boltzmann()} W/(m²·K⁴)")
